dct_description_sm: Map of Cologne and Deutz, now a part of the city of Cologne on the opposite bank of the Rhine, in the German state of North Rhine-Westphalia. Indexed for streets and public buildings. Originally folded in covers 15 x 12 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: Coeln u. Bremen : Verlag von Kraus & Rothe, 1854 (Berlin : Lith. Anst. von W. Hagelberg vorm. Delius)
